  "title": "🔥 Events Sales Rockstar | Weekly Pay | Training Provided 🚀",
  "description": "<p>🎉 <strong>Events Sales Crew | Face-to-Face | No Experience Needed</strong> 🚀</p><p>Love meeting new people? Hate boring desk jobs? Want a role where you can <strong>learn fast, earn weekly, travel, and grow with a solid team</strong>?</p><p>You might be exactly who we’re looking for 👀✨</p><p>We’re building a fun, driven events sales team and want <strong>positive, self-motivated go-getters</strong> who are ready to level up together.</p><p><br /><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p>🤝 Chat with customers face-to-face at events & roadshows</p><p>🎯 Represent brands and close sales in a fun, professional way</p><p>🔥 Learn real-world sales skills on live campaigns</p><p>👯‍♂️ Work closely with a supportive, high-energy team</p><p><br /><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></p><p>🎓 1-to-1 training & daily guidance (we’ve got your back)</p><p>📈 Clear career growth — performance = promotion</p><p>✈️ Travel opportunities (local & overseas 🌍)</p><p>💰 Weekly payouts + incentives</p><p>⚖️ Work-life balance with a team that actually cares</p><p><br /><strong>Who We Want</strong></p><p>⚡ Positive attitude & good vibes</p><p>🗣 Comfortable talking to people (or willing to learn!)</p><p>🌱 Hungry to grow and improve</p><p>🤝 Team players who want to win together<br /></p><p>No experience? No problem. We’ll train you from day one.<br /></p><p>📩 Ready to grow, travel, and build something meaningful?</p><p><strong>Apply now</strong> and let’s make work fun again 🎉🔥</p>",
